<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>matu kampaṇa Uṭaiyārkku Āṉa<unclear>nta</unclear> varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣam</hi> Iruma <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> peruvāy nāṭṭu tiruvēṅkavāyil tā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉattārum Ūravarum pāṭikkāval cuvantaram paṇṇikkuṭutta paricāvatu tiruvēṅkaivācal kuḷam
<lb n="3"/>Uṭaittu pāḻāyk kiṭakkaiyil Itu Ammaittu Iṟaṅkal mīṭkaiyi Ivarkaḷuku māṇikka nēri mi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ppar kuṭikkāṭu peruñcuṉaiyūr vayal maṟavaṉ kāli vayal vaṭamayilāppūr vayal nīkki niṉṟa tēvatāṉa
<lb n="5"/><unclear>U</unclear>ḷ Iṭameṅkum puñcainañcai vakaiyalāl Orukaṭṭum kuḷaccuva <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> paṇṇiṉavaṉ pōṉa tō<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ttilē pōkak kaṭa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vaṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Inta <hi rend="grantha">dharmma</hi> Ācantirā<hi rend="grantha">rkka</hi>māka nayiṉār ceṅkaṇmālī<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>muṭaiya nāyiṉāṟkē naṭatta kaṭavitāka <hi rend="grantha">dā</hi>na <hi rend="grantha">pāla</hi>nayo<hi rend="grantha">rmdhye <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> </hi>
</p>

